<item>
            <title>[LU-23] Improve performance for traversing large directory with readdir+</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-23</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently, we have statahead to improve the performance of traversing large directory, but it is not enough, especially under high network latency environment, we need reduce RPC count under such case. Both aggregate_stat (IT_5) and readdir+ are candidate for that, maybe need to be combined together.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
