                            <comment id="312548" author="adilger" created="Sat, 11 Sep 2021 08:01:01 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Having batched statahead is similar to readdir+ but better in a number of ways.  This can be driven by the client to request attributes for specific FIDs, in a variety of access patterns (e.g. depth-first or breadth-first directory traversal), rather than only sequential readdir.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
